(3) If, as a result of the information provided to him under subsection (1) , or notwithstanding any action taken under subsection (2) , the Registrar is of the opinion that registration is not economically advisable or he is otherwise unwilling to approve registration, he shall give specific reasons therefor to the Minister and to the applicants for registration.
